{"tid":212332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大隻男雙手離地做掌上壓","createTime":"2017-04-22T10:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T11:15:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f881673ca4b45bee2e360f7cce00b34f3f1e3f75","tid":212332,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T10:45:57.000Z","msg":"AM730<br />\n<br />\n大隻男雙手離地做掌上壓？原來同老友出蠱惑(有片)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外國一名高大壯碩男子的健身片段引起網民關注，原因是他竟可完全違反地心吸力，強壯到不用雙手做掌上壓？自稱為「全球最強的磚匠」的他先用雙手做正常的掌上壓，其後再用單手支撐身體，但最離奇的是，最後他甚至可雙手離地，把手交疊於背後，但身體仍可懸空。原來他已把木塊塞到衣服中，再用其支撐身體，並由好友在鏡頭後踩著木板，蹺蹺板般令其身體離地，做出看似超乎常人的掌上壓。<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UIySQcKK38s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUIySQcKK38s&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=1435386b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UIySQcKK38s</a>"},{"pid":"62cc9ec8829d50fa6cd48c1125b46a4737d9094d","tid":212332,"uid":104474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T10:56:12.000Z","msg":"屌 笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e51d4b3485f8325ab803bf43a4f5cf82b3896448","tid":212332,"uid":36026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T11:03:47.000Z","msg":"好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a094618f5bcd2b38cf2714e14da92a473fb368cb","tid":212332,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T11:06:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.dailyder.com/uploads/c4/5/116/14295797897762.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailyder.com%2Fuploads%2Fc4%2F5%2F116%2F14295797897762.jpg&h=c86f8f69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96d81d7d09fa87e3ecffab842fa0d2c2758dfab9","tid":212332,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T11:06:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://www.dailyder.com/uploads/c4/5/116/14295797897762.jpg\" da